title: OneDay for Senior Living

creator: My Lasting Legacy, LLC
descriptionHtml:
OneDay is the most effective way for businesses to create high-quality, personalized videos that drive engagement, conversions, and sales.

HOW IT WORKS:

OneDay helps you create video messages that are authentic, engaging, and effective. It's also easy to use - even if you have no experience.

- Record videos from your mobile or desktop app in just a few clicks, or upload videos directly from your camera roll.
- Make customizations such as trimming your clip, adjusting your thumbnail, changing your theme, and adding music to match your brand standards.
- Send videos by email, social, or however else you communicate. Viewers can watch on any device without worrying about downloading attachments. Even send to contacts integrated with your CRM.
- Detailed analytics dashboards let you see who’s interacting with your videos so you can refine every aspect of your video strategy.
descriptionShort: The ultimate all-in-one personalized video platform.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Convey users can now use OneDay Video for their video creation needs.

Bugfixes
* Fixed issue where it wasn't possible to send videos to recipients of contacts only
* Temporarily disabled magic wand due to some hardware issues on some devices

title: OneDay

creator: My Lasting Legacy, LLC
descriptionHtml:
OneDay is the most effective way for businesses to create high-quality, personalized videos that drive engagement, conversions, and sales.

HOW IT WORKS:

OneDay helps you create video messages that are authentic, engaging, and effective. It's also easy to use - even if you have no experience.

- Record videos from your mobile or desktop app in just a few clicks, or upload videos directly from your camera roll.
- Make customizations such as trimming your clip, adjusting your thumbnail, changing your theme, and adding music to match your brand standards.
- Send videos by email, social, or however else you communicate. Viewers can watch on any device without worrying about downloading attachments. Even send to contacts integrated with your CRM.
- Detailed analytics dashboards let you see who’s interacting with your videos so you can refine every aspect of your video strategy.
descriptionShort: The ultimate all-in-one personalized video platform.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Convey users can now use OneDay for their video creation needs.
Added support for ResMan CRM

Bugfixes
* Fixed a couple crashes around recording videos and selecting contacts.
* Fixed multiple issues where CRM users weren't being shared to properly and not maintaining selection across contact list entries.
* Fixed issue where it wasn't possible to send videos to recipients of contacts only
* Temporarily disabled magic wand due to some hardware issues on some devices

creator: My Lasting Legacy, LLC
descriptionHtml:
OneDay is a cutting-edge platform transforming the way businesses communicate through personalized videos. Our intuitive platform enables seamless recording and editing, perfect for creating high-quality videos on the go (via our mobile app) or in the office (using our desktop solutions). With OneDay, your team can easily align every video with your brand identity.

HOW IT WORKS:
• Recording Made Simple: Capture videos directly on your mobile device or through our desktop platform.
• AI-Powered Script Writing: Leverage our AI ScriptWriter for brand-centric, tailored messaging that resonates with your audience.
• Editing and Customization: Utilize our user-friendly editing tools to add a professional touch to your videos. Choose from a range of themes and music to match your brand's style.
• Seamless CRM Integration: Enhance your sales strategy with our video automation solution, designed to integrate effortlessly with your CRM, aligning your messaging perfectly with your sales process.
• Analytics: With access to our advanced reporting capabilities, you can easily evaluate the success of the program, identify top performs, and proactively adjust messaging to drive more revenue.

Elevate your business storytelling with OneDay. Our platform empowers you to create personalized, brand-aligned videos with ease. Join the video revolution today and see the difference in engagement, conversions, and sales!
descriptionShort: The ultimate all-in-one personalized video platform.
